    "body": "Problem:\r\nThe comma form of 'winborder' is split with copy_option_part(), whose skip_to_option_part() eats spaces after a comma, and empty fields are rejected.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nSplit the comma form literally on ',', keeping empty fields and single-space fields.\r\n\r\nFix #40111 ",
